{{Quote|We welcome all business, you understand, especially that which will prove inconvenient to the Chattza clan or the Empire.|[[Laneet Chekkoo]] of the Chekkoo clan, to [[Luke Skywalker]]|<ref name="Heir to the Jedi" />}}
The '''Chattza clan''' was a [[Rodian]] clan on the [[planet]] [[Rodia]]. The clan was based on the continent opposite to that of [[Betu]]; the Chattza clan had little influence or presence in Betu. They were known to outfit interstellar [[starship]]s.<ref name="Heir to the Jedi" />

During the [[Imperial Era|reign]] of the [[Galactic Empire]], the Chattza clan was the ruling clan of Rodia and one of its members served as the Rodian [[Grand Protector]]. The [[Chekkoo clan]] despised the Chattza clan, and was willing to rebel against the Galactic Empire just to spite them.<ref name="Heir to the Jedi" />

